This press release came through my inbox the other day. Looks like WeMake is doing their own maker conference.  Also, friend of the program, Adam Garcia is the emcee.

>>>Hi there, I wanted to share with you a special event happening for WeMake, the design community, and arts education this fall. 
We are super excited for this amazing line-up. Feel free to share!

Always be making
Yvonne

<http://www.wemakecelebrates.com/>
